title: Sidewall, ca. 1880
creditline: Gift of Mrs. William B. Eldredge
description: Aesthetic-style design, all-over floral and foliette pattern, printed in pink, blue, tan and white, with fine gold outline. Groups of flowers coming out of basket-like containers. Printed on embossed ground.
